01:37:13.000 --> 01:37:23.000
Okay, one of the times he was in, he said he was in for however long, and that he would get letters. Ivan, who said, every day.

01:37:23.000 --> 01:37:31.000
And I said, how did you get them every day? He said, I don't know, but I was getting, he said letters from Ruby Daurus every day.

01:37:31.000 --> 01:37:38.000
Asking how I was doing, just making sure that I knew somebody was taking care of me, was thinking about me and stuff.

01:37:38.000 --> 01:37:50.000
And so Ruby would do that stuff, and also because, you know, she had such an amazing history. I mean, yeah, Jim Foreman, you know, had been just brutalized in LA, and you know, he had been in Monroe, and he had been this and that.

01:37:50.000 --> 01:37:57.000
But Ruby had been in parchment, and Ruby had been in Rock Hill, South Carolina, and those 30 days jail, no bail.

01:37:57.000 --> 01:38:13.000
And also, just Ruby, you know, was just, Ruby had a presence, you know. I mean, when Pennypac says to me, it's worth more, you got to go buy Ruby Daurus to get your application accepted.

