But at least you could expect it, because I remember when I was in Cordial, Georgia, I didn't get it one week. And I had to go to the NA guy who really didn't like my being in town, Cordial in Southwest, Georgia.

01:41:06.000 --> 01:41:20.000
And he ran the restaurant. And I had to say to him, could you just, I don't have enough money for hamburger. But could you just take this whatever little bit I had?

01:41:20.000 --> 01:41:27.000
And he said, I remember saying something about, you know, I'll expect the rest when you get paid. He was not pleasant.

01:41:27.000 --> 01:41:41.000
But I also remember putting a dime in, I spent 30 cents on his jukebox to play Walk On By, Deon War work. But anyway, so.

