See, I got arrested several times in Atlanta demonstrations. That's the thing.

02:11:51.000 --> 02:11:58.000
So, I'm not sure which one was associated with the rest, but the one, if I remember correctly.

02:11:58.000 --> 02:12:01.000
And I'm pretty sure this one was right. The one at the Tattle House.

